data.description: Gorgeous custom home in the highly desirable gated community of Stone House. Homes of this caliber do not come on the market often! Just 2 years young, this home is absolutely better than new! It's like getting a new construction house without the headaches, unexpected costs, supply chain issues or extended build times. Loaded with all the right upgrades, features include a premium 1.2 acre cul-de-sac lot, gourmet kitchen that is a chef's dream come true with a huge island, built in wall oven & microwave, gas cooktop and hood, large pantry, tons of cabinets, beautiful granite countertops, custom backsplash and a sunny dining area, plus a dining room. The family room off the kitchen and the living room both have stunning fireplaces with floor to ceiling tile. Split bedroom plan; Fabulous primary suite with an amazing oversized tiled walk-in shower, extended dual vanities with extra counterspace, center sitting spot, cabinets and drawers...TWO walk in closets, & a private door to the back patio. 2nd and 3rd bedrooms share an upgraded jack and jill bathroom. Den/4th bedroom has double doors and is adjacent to a full bathroom. Nice laundry room with sink, shelves and washer & dryer. Huge private backyard is professionally landscaped and has plenty of room to add a pool, sports court or whatever your heart desires. Custom outdoor built-in BBQ & additional patio area with gas firepit with clear views of the mountains, sunrises and sunsets...perfect for relaxing, entertaining and truly enjoying desert living. Lovely gated front courtyard. Spacious 3 car garage with plenty of room for storage. All that plus Alder wood doors throughout,  top-of-the line window coverings, a security system, surround sound prewire & solar prewire. Check out the video to see an overview of this home and the fabulous surrounding space. Call today for more details and to schedule a showing...don't miss out on this one!
